Class InvalidConstantGuidException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.cyc.base.BaseClientException
          • com.cyc.baseclient.parser.InvalidConstantGuidException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class InvalidConstantGuidException
extends BaseClientException

    Thrown whenever the CycL parser tries to parse a constant by its GuidImpl, and the Cyc server does not already have a constant by that GuidImpl defined.
